result.name: Kingduck

reviews.text: The menu is very interesting. It wanted to try many but in small group of 3, we couldn’t eat much. I enjoyed the pea shoots with air dried eel, chives pancake. Didn’t care for the salted egg prawns, not great for 40$ a piece. The rice fish soup wasn’t great either. But overall, still worth going to and trying something different. Nice decor too. The biggest downside was unkempt toilet.

Shanghai cuisine. Food are pretty good, and appeared to be healthier than what you normally would get dining outside as the dishes were less salty and oily. They employed persons with disability and ethnic minority which is appreciated. But also expect slower service in general. Price a rather expensive too.
Had their afternoon tea set which I think was quite reasonably priced. A bowl of noodles with spare ribs plus an appetizer costed around 68HKD + 10%. Taste is ok.

Don’t come if you have a party of 3-4 people. Most of their tables are for 2, some big ones for 5 or more. Waited for more than an hour, group of 2/6 just walked right in, we were the only group left with endlessness wait. Got rejected when asked if they can combine small tables, or offer us a big one.
Surprising the food taste delicious. Not typical HK style but more to fusion style.

result.name: 京饌

reviews.text: 水準轉差嘅新派京菜館😑
好食👍

下午六時許入坐，70元一客的鮮肉鍋貼上桌時只是微温不熱兼油淋淋，應是將午市之剩餘物資款待晚市客人。
58元一碗的擔擔麵端來時又是不冷不熱，只酸不辣，味道完全不對!
只好即時埋單再到樓上金記醫肚。

The menu is very interesting. It wanted to try many but in small group of 3, we couldn’t eat much. I enjoyed the pea shoots with air dried eel, chives pancake. Didn’t care for the salted egg prawns, not great for 40$ a piece. The rice fish soup wasn’t great either. But overall, still worth going to and trying something different. Nice decor too. The biggest downside was unkempt toilet.
食物可以，但員工態度很一般，問多一句也會miu miu咀...午餐落單後至少等15分鐘以上，仲有識人係可以打尖，仲以為去左茶樓😓最嬲係佢打尖入黎就黎食完，我個碟餸同飯仲未黎

result.name: 創紀之城五期

reviews.text: 路過👍
街117號的港貿中心連接起來，後者電梯大堂亦屬apm管轄範圍。 位處偉業街108號的絲寶國際大廈原為「創紀之城七期」，樓高26層，共提供20層寫字樓及六層停車場。新地於2009年11月發出新聞稿，指這座大廈名為「一號東港」（One Harbour East）。
接連mtr人流高之餘，管理算很完善了
優秀的商業綜合體是東亞銀行總部和APM商場合併而成
觀塘區重建發展得較為成功的項目。
